# Pit Fiend Favored Soul
Weapon and Armor Proficiency	KEY:Pit Fiend Favored Soul ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Pit Fiend Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality			DESC:Pit Fiend Favored souls are proficient with all simple weapons, with light and medium armor, and with shields (except tower shields). A favored soul is also proficient with his diety's favored weapon.  Although a favored soul is not proficient with heavy armor, wearing it does not interfere with her spellcasting.	AUTO:ARMORPROF|ARMORTYPE=Light|ARMORTYPE=Medium	AUTO:SHIELDPROF|SHIELDTYPE=Buckler|SHIELDTYPE=Heavy|SHIELDTYPE=Light	AUTO:WEAPONPROF|DEITYWEAPONS	AUTO:WEAPONPROF|TYPE=Simple	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Weapon Focus			KEY:Pit Fiend Favored Soul ~ Weapon Focus				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Pit Fiend Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality			DESC:At 3rd level, a favored soul gains the Weapon Focus feat with her deity's favored weapon. If the character already has that feat, she can choose a different one.	ADD:ABILITY|FEAT|VIRTUAL|Weapon Focus ~ FS,Weapon Focus Bonus	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Energy Resistance			KEY:Pit Fiend Favored Soul ~ Energy Resistance			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Pit Fiend Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:At 5th level, a favored soul chooses an energy type and gains resistance 10 against that type. At 10th level and 15th level, the character gains resistance 10 against another energy type of her choosing.	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Weapon Specialization		KEY:Pit Fiend Favored Soul ~ Weapon Specialization		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Pit Fiend Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality			DESC:At 12th level, a favored soul gains the Weapon Specialization feat with her deity's favored weapon. If she already has that feat, she can choose a different one.	ADD:ABILITY|FEAT|VIRTUAL|Weapon Specialization ~ FS,Weapon Specialization Bonus	SOURCEPAGE:p.10
Wings					KEY:Pit Fiend Favored Soul ~ Wings					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Pit Fiend Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:At 17th level, a favored soul gains wings and can fly at a speed of 60 feet (good maneuverability). A good-aligned favored soul grows feathered wings, and an evil-aligned favored soul gains batlike wings. A favored soul who is neither good nor evil may choose either type of wings.	BONUS:MOVEADD|TYPE.Fly|60	BONUS:VAR|Maneuverability|3	SOURCEPAGE:p.10
Damage Reduction			KEY:Pit Fiend Favored Soul ~ Damage Reduction			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Pit Fiend Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:A 20th-level favored soul gains damage reduction. If the character is lawful-aligned, the damage reduction is 10/silver. If the character is chaotic-aligned, the damage is 10/cold iron. A favored soul who is neither lawful nor chaotic may choose either type of damage reduction.	DR:10/silver|PREALIGN:LG,LN,LE,NG,TN	DR:10/cold iron|PREALIGN:CG,CN,CE,NE	SOURCEPAGE:p.10

