#Dwarf Racial Traits	KEY:Dwarf Racial Traits	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:EXPORT	DESC:Dwarves can see in the dark up to %1 feet. Darkvision is black and white only, but it is otherwise like normal sight, and dwarves can function just fine with no light at all.|DarkvisionRange|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Darkvision	DESC:&nl;Dwarves may treat dwarven waraxes and dwarven urgroshes as martial weapons, rather than exotic weapons.|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Weapon Familiarity	DESC:&nl;Stonecunning: This ability grants a dwarf a +%1 racial bonus on Search checks to notice unusual stonework, such as sliding walls, stonework traps, new construction (even when built to match the old), unsafe stone surfaces, shaky stone ceilings, and the like. Something that isn't stone but that is disguised as stone also counts as unusual stonework. A dwarf who merely comes within 10 feet of unusual stonework can make a Search check as if he were actively searching, and a dwarf can use the Search skill to find stonework traps as a rogue can. A dwarf can also intuit depth, sensing his approximate depth underground as naturally as a human can sense which way is up.|StonecunningSearchBonus|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Stonecunning	DESC:&nl;Stability: +4 bonus on ability checks made to resist being bull rushed or tripped when standing on the ground (but not when climbing, flying, riding, or otherwise not standing firmly on the ground).|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Stability	DESC:&nl;+%1 racial bonus on saving throws against poison|DwarfPoisonSaveBonus|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Poison Save Bonus	DESC:&nl;+%1 racial bonus on saving throws against spells and spell-like effects|DwarfSpellSaveBonus|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Spell Save Bonus	DESC:&nl;+%1 racial bonus on attack rolls against orcs and goblinoids|DwarfRacialCombatBonus|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Attack Bonus	DESC:&nl;+%1 Dodge bonus to Armor Class against monsters of the giant type|DwarfDodgeGiantBonus|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Dodge Bonus	DESC:&nl;+%1 racial bonus on Appraise checks that are related to stone or metal items.|DwarfAppraiseSkillBonus|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Appraise Bonus	DESC:&nl;+%1 racial bonus on Craft checks that are related to stone or metal.|DwarfCraftSkillBonus|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dwarf ~ Craft Bonus
